4. Sorting and reversing an array.
  Type	Method
  a. Primitive: int[]	=>   sort + reverse   , Can be directly reversed
  b. Object[] : Integer[] => 	Arrays.sort(arr, reverseOrder) , Can be directly reversed through ,
                                Arrays.sort And Collections.reverseOrder
  c. Stream array :Stream	=> boxed + sorted
                                Arrays.stream(int[]).boxed()
                                .sorted(Collections.reverseOrder)
                                .mapToInt(Integer::intValue)
                                .toArray

